text: Carlos Enrique de Castro Storace (, 19 April 1979 – 16 February 2015) was an Uruguayan footballer who played as a centre back. ==Club career== He previously also played abroad for Deportes Melipilla from Chile, Club San José from Bolivia, and Thrasyvoulos F.C. of Greece. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:2015 deaths Category:Association football defenders Category:Chilean Primera División players Category:Club San José players Category:Deportes Melipilla footballers Category:Expatriate footballers in Bolivia Category:Expatriate footballers in Chile Category:Miramar Misiones players Category:FC Luzern players Category:Sportspeople from Montevideo Category:Thrasyvoulos F.C. players Category:Uruguayan footballers Category:Uruguayan expatriate footballers Category:Uruguayan expatriate sportspeople in Bolivia Category:Uruguayan expatriate sportspeople in Chile Category:Uruguayan expatriate sportspeople in Greece Category:Expatriate footballers in Greece
